Responsibly sourced 

Sainsbury's Scottish Taste the Difference salmon is sourced from specialty selected locations around the West of Scotland. The farms use responsibly management practices and our salmon are fed a bespoked diet designed to both protect our natural resources from over fishing and guarantee great taste and nutritional benefit for you. 

 

RSPCA Assured 

The salmon in this product comes from producers inspected to RSPCA welfare standards by RSPCA's independently certified farm assurance scheme.  

For more information visit www.rspcaassured.org.uk/sainsburys
